OL,3,CEx-miners call on government to
OL,4,Crelease #2.3bn of pension payments
OL,6,FFormer mineworkers are lobbying the
OL,7,Fgovernment to release #2.3 billion in
OL,8,Freserves from a pension scheme to
OL,9,Funlock extra retirement payments.
OL,11,FSix members of the British Coal Staff
OL,12,FSuperannuation Scheme visited
OL,13,FWestminster on Monday to call on the
OL,14,FIndustry Minister to intervene.
OL,16,FEx-miner Peter Short told ITV
OL,17,FCalendar: "We kept the lights on in
OL,18,Fthis country for many years, which was
OL,19,Fdirty dangerous work.
