OL,4,Crelease #2.3bn of pension payments
OL,6,F"It would mean a fantastic amount that
OL,7,Fin old age, in poverty and in illness,
OL,8,Fthat we are able to get the benefits
OL,9,Fwe deserve."
OL,11,FAt last year's budget, it was
OL,12,Fannounced a similar investment
OL,13,Freserve, the Mineworkers Pension
OL,14,FScheme, would be released to
OL,15,Fpensioners.
OL,17,FThat meant #1.5 billion was
OL,18,Ftransferred leading to an average
OL,19,Fweekly increase of #29 for members.
