OL,3,CEx-miners call on government to
OL,4,Crelease #2.3bn of pension payments
OL,6,FAnother former mineworker, Andy
OL,7,FSearson, wants the Chancellor to use
OL,8,Fthis year's budget to do the same for
OL,9,Fthe 40,000 BCSSS members.
OL,11,F"This is not the government's money,
OL,12,Fit belongs to the pensioners" he said.
OL,14,FHe added that members of the scheme
OL,15,Fwere dying before getting any
OL,16,Fadditional funds.
