OL,3,CEx-miners call on government to
OL,4,Crelease #2.3bn of pension payments
OL,6,F"My friend died, he was 75, he died
OL,7,Fonly last year and he has not seen any
OL,8,Fof this additional money which would
OL,9,Fhave made his life a little bit better
OL,10,Ftowards the end," he said.
OL,12,F"In the Mansfield area, there are
OL,13,Fthousands of people who need this
OL,14,Fmoney."
OL,16,FThe scheme began in 1947 but,
OL,17,Ffollowing the privatisation of the
OL,18,Fcoal industry in 1994, the government
OL,19,Fbecame a guarantor for the BCSSS.
