OL,3,CEx-miners call on government to
OL,4,Crelease #2.3bn of pension payments
OL,6,FMansfield's Labour MP Steve Yemm said:
OL,7,F"I've discussed this with ministers
OL,8,Fright around the government - I'm
OL,9,Fsaying respect what these people did.
OL,11,F"They powered our country, they dug
OL,12,Fcoal out of the ground and it's time
OL,13,Fthey got what is rightfully theirs."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,16,FEnergy Security and Net Zero said: "We
OL,17,Fare talking to the Treasury about
OL,18,Fproposals from trustees of the scheme
OL,19,Fand will provide an update in due
OL,20,Fcourse."
